            "value": "<h1><strong>Version History</strong></h1><table class=\"relative-table\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 62.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 132.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 84.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 102.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 120.0px;\" /></colgroup><thead><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Name</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Date</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Reviewer&nbsp;</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>&nbsp;Description</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Document Referred</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Rudya S</strong></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><time datetime=\"2024-04-22\" /><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></div></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Mubarak</strong></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Created the API to offer attachment Details.</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>MTN&nbsp; Ivory Coast SOA Specifications Document_v3.24</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><h1><strong>API Description</strong></h1><p><strong>This API can be used to offer attachment details.</strong></p><p><br /></p><table class=\"relative-table\" style=\"width: 555.646px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 72.75px;\" /><col style=\"width: 482.229px;\" /></colgroup><thead><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>South Bound</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>API Details</strong></p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>3PP</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33,33,33);\"><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://10.4.3.95:7001/api/v1/customer-management/terminate\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">http://10.4.3.95:1221/offersubscription/v1/cs/charging/offer</a></span></strong></p></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Method</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>POST</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 class=\"auto-cursor-target\"><strong>North bound details</strong></h2><p><strong>This API will be consumed by&nbsp;3PP.</strong></p><h1><strong>Technical Detail</strong></h1><h3><strong>HTTP METHOD</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>POST</strong></li></ul><h3><strong>URL</strong></h3><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33,33,33);\"><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://mtngodc.ace.dev-rancher.tecnotree.com/dap-is/termination?lob=HPBX\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">https://{DAP_HOSTNAME}/dap-is/offerAttachment_TSAT</a></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0);\">Note:<span>&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0);\">The host name of the endpoints is subject to change according to the environment it is deployed.</span></p><h2><strong>Input Parameters</strong></h2><table class=\"relative-table\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 141.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 229.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 123.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 94.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 187.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 89.0px;\" /></colgroup><thead><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Parameter Name</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Description</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Parameter Type</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Mandatory</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Sample Value</p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p>Data Type</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>subscriberNumber</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">Represents the&nbsp;publicIdentifier/subscriberNumber</span></strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Request</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Y</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>9876543211</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>String</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\"><strong>OfferId</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">Represents the&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>OfferId</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\"><strong>Request</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\"><strong>Y</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\"><strong>20390</strong></td><td colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>String</strong></span></td></tr></tbody></table><h2><strong>Output Parameters</strong></h2><table class=\"relative-table\"><thead><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Parameter Name</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Description</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Parameter Type</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Sample Value</strong></p></th><th style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Data Type</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>responseCode</strong></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Represents the code</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Response</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>0</strong></span></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>string</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><br /></p><p><strong>responseMessage</strong></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Represents the message returned for the response</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Response</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>Success</strong></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>string</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>createdOn</strong></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Represents the date of creation and time</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Response</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">2022-07-10T05:57:01</span></strong></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>String</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong>transactionId</strong></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Represents the transaction Id</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>Response</strong></span></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">1000</span></strong></p><p><br /></p></td><td style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,51,102);\"><strong>String</strong></span></td></tr></thead></table><h1><strong>Sample Request</strong></h1><p><br /><br /><br /></p><table class=\"relative-table\" style=\"width: 437.037px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 0.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th style=\"text-align: left;\">{<br />&quot;clientRequest&quot;: {<br />&quot;EaiEnvelope&quot;: {<br />&quot;ApplicationName&quot;: &quot;MTNN&quot;,<br />&quot;Domain&quot;: &quot;EIA&quot;,<br />&quot;Service&quot;: &quot;Cs3Services&quot;,<br />&quot;OperationName&quot;: &quot;active&quot;,<br />&quot;Sender&quot;: &quot;testuser3&quot;,<br />&quot;MessageId&quot;: 1616752614124,<br />&quot;Lan